<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَاعَةِ الْعُسْرَةِ}</span> ... وَقْتِ الشِّدَّةِ،<span class="c5"> وَالمُرَادُ:</span> غَزْوَةُ تَبُوكٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَزِيغُ}</span> ... يَمِيلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمَا رَحُبَتْ}</span> ... مَعَ رَحْبِهَا وَسَعَتِهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يَرْغَبُوا بِأَنفُسِهِمْ عَن نَّفْسِهِ}</span> ... بِأَنْ لَّا يَرْضَوْا بِالرَّاحَةِ لِأَنْفُسِهِمْ مَعَ تَعَبِهِ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
