<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَخْمَصَةٌ}</span> ... مَجَاعَةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَغِيظُ}</span> ... يُغْضِبُ، وَيُغِمُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّيْلًا}</span> ... قَتْلًا، أَوْ هَزِيمَةً، أو أذًى.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِيَنفِرُوا كَافَّةً}</span> ... لِيَخْرُجُوا لِلْجِهَادِ جَمِيعًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
